{"word":"G5074 - τετράπους - tetrápous - tet-rap'-ooce - Fourfooted beast","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">τετράπους</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">tetrápous</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">tet-rap'-ooce</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Fourfooted beast</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"நாலுகால் - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"four - footed"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G5064 - τέσσαρες - téssares - tes'-sar-es/5064\">G5064</a> and <a href=\"#/G4228 - πούς - poús - pooce/4228\">G4228</a>; a <i>quadruped:</i> - fourfooted beast.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G5062/5062\">G5062</a>, <a href=\"#/G5063/5063\">G5063</a>, <a href=\"#/G5064/5064\">G5064</a>, <a href=\"#/G5065/5065\">G5065</a>, <a href=\"#/G5066/5066\">G5066</a>, <a href=\"#/G5067/5067\">G5067</a>, <a href=\"#/G5068/5068\">G5068</a>, <a href=\"#/G5069/5069\">G5069</a>, <a href=\"#/G5070/5070\">G5070</a>, <a href=\"#/G5071/5071\">G5071</a>, <a href=\"#/G5072/5072\">G5072</a>, <a href=\"#/G5073/5073\">G5073</a>, <a href=\"#/G5074/5074\">G5074</a>, <a href=\"#/G5075/5075\">G5075</a>, <a href=\"#/G5076/5076\">G5076</a>"}]}